The function \( f(n) \) is defined as:
\[
f(n) = n^2 + n + 17
\]

\[
f(12) = 12^2 + 12 + 17

\[
12^2 = 144

\]

\[
11^2 = 121
\]

\[

\]

\[
f(12) - f(11) = 173 - 149 = 24
\]

\[
\boxed{24}
